 doctor who used paddis for his baby helped change medical opinion and they began to be stocked by boots image copyright hunter gordon family image caption valerie hunter gordon with her daughter frances in another early paddi advertisement they were advertised as a really attractive garment skilfully designed by a mother to make the wholetime use of disposable nappies a practical possibilitythe company eventually went into decline in the s with the arrival of the american brand pampersmrs hunter gordons daughter frances ross said her mother had been survived by six children  grandchildren and  greatgrandchildren with another due in a few months related topics babies  toddlers share this story about sharing email facebook messenger messenger twitter pinterest whatsapp linkedin top stories shooting at israeli embassy in jordan a jordanian is killed and two others wounded including an israeli in the incident in amman  july  white house uncertainty over russia bill  july  rio protest over brazil police deaths  july  features video texas county struggles with migrant deaths trying the huntergatherer berry and porcupine diet animal v athlete four times man has raced beast video the rather rude sounds of an elephant seal south koreas female golfing phenomenon six unpresidented months   to go the first irish immigrant deported by trump video can writing a letter change a life could trump pardon himself news navigation bbc news services on your mobile on your connected tv get news alerts contact bbc news explore the bbc home home news news sport weather shop earth travel capital iplayer culture autos future tv radio cbbc cbeebies food iwonder bitesize travel music earth arts make it digital taster nature local littelfuse inc  board of directors english chinese german japanese find authorized distributors contact us about littelfuse partner login littelfuse business center littelfuse university electronics intranet search all battery management dc solenoids and relays electr